p:
Protein expression plots were exported from the human protein atlas ( https://www.proteinatlas.org/)
60 to determine whether there is evidence of protein expression of viral entry genes. ACE2 was probed by two antibodies (HPA000288 and CAB026174), TMPRSS2 was probed by one antibody (HPA035787), and CTSL was probed by one antibody (CAB000459).
